{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_bdrk_01GdEbFFcghpaxdPPQHPAEo2","type":"tool_result","content":"( ( )\\___ | '_ | '_| | '_ \\/ _` | \\ \\ \\ \\\n \\\\/  ___)| |_)| | | | | || (_| |  ) ) ) )\n  '  |____| .__|_| |_|_| |_\\__, | / / / /\n =========|_|==============|___/=/_/_/_/\n :: Spring Boot ::                (v3.2.5)\n\n2026-03-17T00:47:59.620Z  INFO 1 --- [           main] c.e.addressbook.AddressBookApplication   : Starting AddressBookApplication v1.0-SNAPSHOT using Java 21.0.10 with PID 1 (/app/target/address-book-1.0-SNAPSHOT.jar started by root in /app)\n2026-03-17T00:47:59.634Z  INFO 1 --- [           main] c.e.addressbook.AddressBookApplication   : No active profile set, falling back to 1 default profile: \"default\"\n2026-03-17T00:48:00.839Z  INFO 1 --- [           main] .s.d.r.c.RepositoryConfigurationDelegate : Bootstrapping Spring Data JPA repositories in DEFAULT mode.\n2026-03-17T00:48:00.908Z  INFO 1 --- [           main] .s.d.r.c.RepositoryConfigurationDelegate : Finished Spring Data repository scanning in 56 ms. Found 1 JPA repository interface.\n2026-03-17T00:48:01.591Z  INFO 1 --- [           main] o.s.b.w.embedded.tomcat.TomcatWebServer  : Tomcat initialized with port 8080 (http)\n2026-03-17T00:48:01.606Z  INFO 1 --- [           main] o.apache.catalina.core.StandardService   : Starting service [Tomcat]\n2026-03-17T00:48:01.606Z  INFO 1 --- [           main] o.apache.catalina.core.StandardEngine    : Starting Servlet engine: [Apache Tomcat/10.1.20]\n2026-03-17T00:48:01.646Z  INFO 1 --- [           main] o.a.c.c.C.[Tomcat].[localhost].[/]       : Initializing Spring embedded WebApplicationContext\n2026-03-17T00:48:01.647Z  INFO 1 --- [           main] w.s.c.ServletWebServerApplicationContext : Root WebApplicationContext: initialization completed in 1795 ms\n2026-03-17T00:48:01.698Z  INFO 1 --- [           main] com.zaxxer.hikari.HikariDataSource       : HikariPool-1 - Starting...\n2026-03-17T00:48:02.077Z  INFO